  "page": "Merion",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Maesters\" title=\"Maesters\"><img alt=\"Grand Maester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/65/Grand_Maester.svg/50px-Grand_Maester.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/65/Grand_Maester.svg/75px-Grand_Maester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/65/Grand_Maester.svg/100px-Grand_Maester.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Grand Maester</span><br />Merion</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Maesters\" title=\"Maesters\"><img alt=\"Grand Maester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/65/Grand_Maester.svg/50px-Grand_Maester.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/65/Grand_Maester.svg/75px-Grand_Maester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/65/Grand_Maester.svg/100px-Grand_Maester.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Grand_Maester\" title=\"Grand Maester\">Grand Maester</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\nThe <a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">Citadel</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_192_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">192&#160;AC</a> or <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_193_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">193&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Calculation_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Calculation-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/259_AC\" title=\"259 AC\">259&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Calculation_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Calculation-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><br />The <a href=\"/index.php/Roseroad\" title=\"Roseroad\">roseroad</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Merion</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Grand_Maester\" title=\"Grand Maester\">Grand Maester</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">Citadel</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Merion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Merion was made <a href=\"/index.php/Grand_Maester\" title=\"Grand Maester\">Grand Maester</a> at the age of sixty-six and sent to serve the court of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_V_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon V Targaryen\">Aegon V Targaryen</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> to succeed Grand Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Ellendor\" title=\"Ellendor\">Ellendor</a>. He died on his way to King's Landing and was succeeded by Grand Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Pycelle\" title=\"Pycelle\">Pycelle</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Merion's work <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Red_Dragon_and_the_Black\" title=\"The Red Dragon and the Black\">The Red Dragon and the Black</a></i> was left unfinished.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_daeron_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_daeron_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Merion once referred to the custom of <a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lys</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Myr\" title=\"Myr\">Myr</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrosh\" title=\"Tyrosh\">Tyrosh</a> to grant licenses on ships to prey upon those of their foes as \"<a href=\"/index.php/Piracy\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Piracy\">piracy</a> with a <a href=\"/index.php/Wax\" title=\"Wax\">wax</a> seal\".<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_quarrelsome_daughters:_myr.2C_lys.2C_and_tyrosh.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_quarrelsome_daughters:_myr.2C_lys.2C_and_tyrosh.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Merion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\" style=\"-webkit-column-width:200px; -moz-column-width:200px; column-width:200px; -webkit-column-count:2; -moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Calculation-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Calculation_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"